<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<section 
  xml:id="ch-i_sec-instructor-intro" 
  label="ch-i_sec-instructor-intro" 
  xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
  >
  <title>To The Instructor</title>

  <p> 
    Introduction for the instructor goes here.  This will include an overview, advice on picking a KitClient and the deploy instructions.
  </p>

  <p>
    Click the following link to
    
    <url href="https://gitpod.io/?autostart=true#https://github.com/hfossedu/gitkit-deployer-gitpod" 
    visual="gitpod.io/?autostart=true#https://github.com/hfossedu/gitkit-deployer-gitpod">
      Deploy the GitKit
    </url>
  </p>

  <p>
    Instructor guide informatoin will appear in the instructor version of the document as follows:

    <tabular top="major" bottom="major" left="major" right="major">
      <row>
        <cell>
          <image source="images/shared-images/instructor-info" width="40%">
            <description>
              Instructor icon that indicates instructor guide information.
            </description>
          </image> 
        </cell>
        <cell>
          <p>
            Information for the instructor appears here and will typically be long enough to shrink the column on the left down to the size of the icon.
          </p>
        </cell>
      </row>
    </tabular>
  </p>

  <p> 
    For example the instructor information below will not appear if the <em>web</em> or <em>print</em> source is built.

    <commentary component="instructor">
      <tabular top="major" bottom="major" left="major" right="major">
        <row>
          <cell>
            <image source="images/shared-images/instructor-info" width="40%">
              <description>
                Instructor icon that indicates instructor guide information.
              </description>
            </image> 
          </cell>
          <cell>
            <p>
              Information for the instructor appears here and will typically be long enough to shrink the column on the left down to the size of the icon.
            </p>
          </cell>
        </row>
      </tabular>
    </commentary>
  </p>
  
</section>